{"tid":1634334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"cc台不如同講故台合併","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:17:50.000Z","uid":234509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"054987360fc1f4be61c34863ba876bf23bbf7dbc","tid":1634334,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:29:19.000Z","msg":"幾秒後，有手足追上黎，唔知咩事一野就打爆個收銀機。然後有個肥仔沖去亂拳打個收銀員，仲大叫：「香港民主大於一切。」<br />\n<br />\n之後有個年紀較細嘅拎住個鎚仔一鎚扑落個收銀到，話：「我代民主同自由懲罰你！」<br />\n<br />\n然後成班一路嗌住光復香港，時代革命搶走晒店舖入面嘅食物<br />\n<br />\n依家前線真係失撚晒控<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631568</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7642386bd56529c7f083c34f0122879394478ef","tid":1634334,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣係五毛來，我前同事"},{"pid":"71262fcb24e38e8b641df1ef870fa5e71d05be7d","tid":1634334,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"假到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92afa917dd36d2cbe8ccfdcdbb17801469198ff","tid":1634334,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7642386bd56529c7f083c34f0122879394478ef","tid":1634334,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣係五毛來，我前同事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:59:26.000Z","msg":"呢條都係"},{"pid":"f4eba0110381a50ba4872d71816f97796e9b522a","tid":1634334,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score